data.name: label1.Text
data.value: LaserGRBL tracks the useful life of your lasers, to let you know how much each laser module has been used. If you have more than one machine or laser module you can add them with the "add" button. In this case LaserGRBL will ask you which laser you are using at the time of connection, so as to assign consumption to the right module each time.
